    <h3>4. Payments</h3>
    <p>Premium playlist sets require a one-time curation fee, processed securely through Stripe. Fees are non-refundable once a set is unlocked, except as required by law. Pricing is displayed in USD and may vary by set (e.g., $5 or higher). You are responsible for any additional taxes or fees imposed by your payment provider.</p>

