    <p>We may suspend or terminate your access to Hip Hop Grammar for violating these Terms or at our discretion. You can stop using the service at any time by logging out and deleting saved playlists from Spotify.</p>

    <h3>9. Changes to Terms</h3>
    <p>We may update these Terms periodically. Continued use of Hip Hop Grammar after changes constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms. Check this page for the latest version.</p>

    <h3>10. Contact Us</h3>
    <p>For questions or support, email us at <a href="mailto:support@illegible.ink" class="external-link">support@illegible.ink</a>.</p>

    <p>Last updated: April 6, 2025</p>
  </div>

  <footer class="footer">
    <form action="/delete-data" method="POST"><button type="submit" class="delete-button">Delete My Data</button></form>
    <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
    <a href="/terms">Terms of Use</a>
    <span>Powered by<a href="https://www.spotify.com" target="_blank"><img src="/logo.svg" alt="Spotify" class="footer-logo"></a></span>
